headline: Dow Jones Leader Plows To New Highs As Gold Stock Glows
summary: Caterpillar plowed its way to an all-time high just ahead of earnings this week. Kinross Gold also scored a high after earnings.

headline: AEP expects to add 24 GW of load by 2030, mainly from data centers
summary: More than half of the pending load is in Texas, where AEP Texas is set to interconnect 5 GW of cryptocurrency operations, per William Fehrman, AEP president and CEO.

headline: 2 Utilities That Stand to Gain From Big Tech’s Power Play
summary: Entergy and American Electric Power are well-positioned to service power-hungry data centers while skirting a regulatory backlash.
